        <h2 id="title">About RailYatri</h2>
        <h3>Your Trusted Train Booking Application</h3>
        <p>Welcome to <strong>RailYatri</strong>, your trusted train booking application! RailYatri is designed to make your train travel experience simple, convenient, and enjoyable. Whether you are a daily commuter, a tourist, or someone planning a long journey, RailYatri has everything you need to ensure a smooth and hassle-free travel experience.</p>

        <h4>Our Vision</h4>
        <p>At RailYatri, we aim to revolutionize the way people book train tickets by offering a user-friendly platform that combines efficiency with ease of use. Our goal is to simplify train travel for every passenger, ensuring they spend more time planning their trips and less time worrying about logistics.</p>

        <h4>Features of RailYatri</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Seamless Train Booking:</strong> Quick and efficient ticket booking in just a few clicks.</li>
            <li><strong>Live Train Information:</strong> Real-time updates on train schedules, delays, and cancellations.</li>
            <li><strong>Passenger-Friendly Interface:</strong> Clean and intuitive design for effortless navigation.</li>
            <li><strong>Booking Management:</strong> Easy view, edit, and cancel options for your bookings.</li>
            <li><strong>Personalized Services:</strong> Save preferences, passenger details, and favorite routes.</li>
            <li><strong>Secure Payment Options:</strong> Safe and reliable payment gateways.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>Why Choose RailYatri?</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Convenience:</strong> Book train tickets anytime, anywhere.</li>
            <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> Accurate schedules and real-time alerts.</li>
            <li><strong>Affordable:</strong> Transparent pricing with no hidden charges.</li>
            <li><strong>Customer Support:</strong> Dedicated assistance for all queries and issues.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>How RailYatri Works</h4>
        <ol>
            <li>Search for Trains: Enter your origin, destination, and travel date to get a list of available trains.</li>
            <li>Select Your Train: Choose the train and class that best suits your needs.</li>
            <li>Enter Passenger Details: Provide passenger information and seat preferences.</li>
            <li>Make Payment: Complete your booking with our secure payment gateway.</li>
            <li>Get Your Ticket: Receive your e-ticket instantly via email or SMS.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>We look forward to being a part of your journey. Happy traveling with RailYatri!</p>
